flowchart LR
    C[客户端] --> G[API Gateway]
    G --> A[Go 秒杀接入服务]

    A -->|Lua 原子预占| R[(Redis)]
    A -->|同步有界发送| MQ[(RocketMQ)]

    R --> RS[Reservation 补发扫描器]
    RS -->|相同 message_id 补发| MQ

    MQ --> OC[订单消费者]
    OC -->|本地事务| PG[(PostgreSQL)]

    PG --> IB[consumer_inbox]
    PG --> ORD[orders / inventory]
    PG --> OB[event_outbox]

    OC -->|事务提交后 ACK| MQ
    OC -->|最佳努力更新| R

    OB --> OP[Outbox Publisher]
    OP --> DMQ[延迟取消 Topic]
    DMQ --> CC[超时取消消费者]
    CC --> PG

    MQ --> DLQ[Dead Letter Queue]
    DLQ --> DP[DLQ 处置与回放平台]
    DP --> MQ
